'''Instructional animations''' are [[animation]]s that are used either to provide instructions for immediate performance of a task or to support more permanent [[education|learning]] of subject matter. While both of these uses can be described as instructional animations, when the goal is to support learning, the term [[educational animation]] may be preferred.

