The '''École nationale des sciences appliquées de Fès(ENSAF)''' is a public engineering school located in [[Fes|Fez]], part of the national network of schools of applied sciences-[[Écoles nationales des sciences appliquées|ENSA]] of [[Morocco]]. It was created in 2005 and follows a 5 year course structure.
==Programs offered== *Computer engineering *Telecommunication and Networks engineering *Industrial engineering *Mechanical engineering and automate systems. *Embedded systems and industrial computing.
==External links== * [http://www.ensaf.ac.ma Site officiel]
